column5: Hey We bought 3 Automatic Cooler/Chillers for this years In School Hatcheries & Automatic feeders for the Weekends & Holidays, both Schools are very excited to see them set up & the Hatch started  Check it out SBK  LHFC School Hatchery & Event Blog

im very happy to see you are going to do this again SBK....good luck with this years school of fish and school of kids...i commend you for your efforts...there are some outstanding characters on this forum ...and you sir.....are one of them!
